/Primeros 10 multiplos de 7
ORG 000


		Load Zero
		StoreI P1

Loop,	LoadI P1
		Add BASE
		Output
		Store Var
		Load P1
		Add One
		Store P1
		Load Var
		StoreI P1
		Load CONT
		Subt One
		Store CONT
		SkipCond 400
		Jump Loop
		Halt
		
P1, HEX 0050
BASE, DEC 7
CONT, DEC 10
One, DEC 1
Zero, DEC 0
Var, DEC 10
